55:20.526 --> 55:22.437
You've heard all about these people
but you never met them.

55:24.071 --> 55:25.106
Good for the book.

55:28.283 --> 55:29.318
Find a window.

55:30.452 --> 55:31.442
Pounce.

55:32.371 --> 55:33.361
