Thomas?

01:02:32.832 --> 01:02:34.288
Thomas, what are you doing?

01:02:36.002 --> 01:02:36.992
It's raining.

01:02:44.052 --> 01:02:45.087
Okay.

01:02:47.555 --> 01:02:48.590
I...

01:02:49.349 --> 01:02:50.430
I broke up with Nick...

01:02:52.185 --> 01:02:54.722
